commitResults.messageBody:
This commit introduces basic error and exception handling for user commands (mark, unmark, deadline, todo).

It also sets up the initial package structure:
- clod: Main chatbot class and related logic
- exceptions: Custom exception classes
- operations: Task-related classes (Task, Todo, Deadline, Event, TaskList)
